  24 Aug 2013; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> rabbit-1.0.9.ebuild:
  add ~x86, bug #415151

  11 Aug 2013; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop package from ruby herd as per 2013-07-21 announcement.

  31 Aug 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rabbit-1.0.6.ebuild,
  -rabbit-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

*rabbit-1.0.9 (27 Jul 2012)

  27 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-1.0.9.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  21 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rabbit-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Add rdtool as a build dependency with USE=emacs to properly fix bug 426924.

*rabbit-1.0.8 (20 Jul 2012)

  20 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fix dependency on rdtool to match emacs USE flag, fixing bug
  426924.

  16 Jun 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> rabbit-0.9.2.ebuild,
  rabbit-1.0.6.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Use global USE flag "postscript" instead of local USE flag "gs" for
  PostScript support

  19 May 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rabbit-1.0.6.ebuild:
  Reverse order since the USE=emacs code cd's into a directory.. Fixes problem
  reported in bug 415151.

*rabbit-1.0.6 (08 May 2012)

  08 May 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-1.0.6.ebuild:
  Version bump. Drop x86 due to new dependency on kramdown, bug 415151.

  26 Dec 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rabbit-0.6.4-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

*rabbit-0.9.2 (07 May 2011)

  07 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-0.9.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  12 Mar 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rabbit-0.6.4-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Drop gnome-print USE flag and dependency. No longer supported since 0.5.3.
  Bug 358417.

  12 Mar 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rabbit-0.6.3.ebuild,
  -rabbit-0.6.4.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

*rabbit-0.6.4-r1 (14 Jul 2010)

  14 Jul 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-0.6.4-r1.ebuild:
  Convert to ruby-ng.

*rabbit-0.6.4 (27 Feb 2010)

  27 Feb 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +rabbit-0.6.4.ebuild:
